sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant V as Vue Page
    participant S as Pinia Store
    participant P as PromoCode Map

    U->>V: Enter code + click Apply
    V->>S: applyPromoCode("SAVE10")
    S->>P: Look up code
    alt Code found
        P-->>S: { type: "percentage", value: 10 }
        S->>S: Check minSubtotal
        alt Subtotal qualifies
            S-->>S: Set appliedPromoCode
            S-->>V: discount getter updates
            V-->>U: Show success + discount line
        else Subtotal too low
            S-->>V: Set promoError
            V-->>U: Show error message
        end
    else Code not found
        P-->>S: undefined
        S-->>V: Set promoError
        V-->>U: Show "Invalid code" error
    end

    U->>V: Click Remove
    V->>S: removePromoCode()
    S-->>V: discount = 0
    V-->>U: Show input field again